---
---

<section class="section subsidies-section" id="finantare">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="fin-header animate-on-scroll">
      <span class="section-eyebrow light">Opțiuni de finanțare</span>
      <h2 class="subsidies-title font-display">
        Nu trebuie să plătești<br />totul dintr-o dată.
      </h2>
      <p class="subsidies-intro">
        Instalezi acum, panourile încep să producă imediat. Rata lunară poate fi acoperită chiar din economia la factură.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="subsidies-grid">
      <!-- TBI Bank — principal -->
      <div class="fin-card fin-card--primary animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="fin-card-badge">Disponibil acum</div>
        <div class="fin-card-logo">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#F5A623" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M11.8 10.9c-2.27-.59-3-1.2-3-2.15 0-1.09 1.01-1.85 2.7-1.85 1.78 0 2.44.85 2.5 2.1h2.21c-.07-1.72-1.12-3.3-3.21-3.81V3h-3v2.16c-1.94.42-3.5 1.68-3.5 3.61 0 2.31 1.91 3.46 4.7 4.13 2.5.6 3 1.48 3 2.41 0 .69-.49 1.79-2.7 1.79-2.06 0-2.87-.92-2.98-2.1h-2.2c.12 2.19 1.76 3.42 3.68 3.83V21h3v-2.15c1.95-.37 3.5-1.5 3.5-3.55 0-2.84-2.43-3.81-4.7-4.4z"/></svg>
          Finanțare prin TBI Bank
        </div>
        <h3 class="fin-card-title font-display">Plătești în rate.<br />Panourile plătesc rata.</h3>
        <p class="fin-card-text">
          Prin parteneriatul nostru cu TBI Bank, poți finanța întregul sistem — panouri, invertor, structură, instalare —
          în rate lunare fixe. Fără avans, fără birocrație, cu aprobare online în aceeași zi.
        </p>

        <div class="tbi-stats">
          <div class="tbi-stat">
            <span class="tbi-stat-val font-display">0%</span>
            <span class="tbi-stat-label">Avans</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tbi-stat">
            <span class="tbi-stat-val font-display">60</span>
            <span class="tbi-stat-label">Rate max.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tbi-stat">
            <span class="tbi-stat-val font-display">1 zi</span>
            <span class="tbi-stat-label">Aprobare</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <ul class="fin-checks">
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#F5A623" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
            Credit până la 30.000 EUR — acoperă kituri complete
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#F5A623" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
            Rate fixe — buget previzibil pe toată perioada
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#F5A623" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
            Aprobare 100% online, în aceeași zi
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#F5A623" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
            Disponibil persoane fizice cu venituri stabile
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/cerere-oferta" class="subsidies-cta">
          Solicită ofertă cu finanțare inclusă
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <p class="subsidies-note">Îți prezentăm opțiunile la prima consultație — gratuit.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- AFM — secundar, viitor -->
      <div class="fin-card fin-card--secondary animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="fin-card-badge fin-card-badge--future">Estimat toamna 2026</div>
        <div class="fin-card-logo fin-card-logo--dim">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 14.5v-9l6 4.5-6 4.5z"/></svg>
          Grant Casa Verde AFM
        </div>
        <h3 class="fin-card-title font-display">20.000 RON<br />nerambursabili de la stat.</h3>
        <p class="fin-card-text">
          Programul AFM Casa Verde Fotovoltaice este în așteptare pentru 2026. Pe baza edițiilor anterioare,
          înscrierile sunt estimate pentru <strong>septembrie–octombrie 2026</strong>. Ghidul de finanțare
          urmează să fie publicat de AFM după deblocarea bugetului.
        </p>
        <div class="afm-info-box">
          <strong>Ce știm până acum:</strong>
          <ul>
            <li>Finanțare de până la 20.000 RON per gospodărie</li>
            <li>Posibil accent pe baterii de stocare în 2026</li>
            <li>Fondurile tind să se epuizeze rapid la deschidere</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="/subventii-casa-verde" class="subsidies-check-btn">
          Cum te pregătești din timp
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .subsidies-section {
    background: #1E6B3A;
    color: white;
  }

  .fin-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .section-eyebrow.light {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  }

  .subsidies-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .subsidies-intro {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .subsidies-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .subsidies-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
  }

  .fin-card {
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .fin-card--primary {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  }

  .fin-card--secondary {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .fin-card-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    background: #F5A623;
    color: #1A1A1A;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .fin-card-badge--future {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  }

  .fin-card-logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .fin-card-logo--dim {
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .fin-card-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: white;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .fin-card-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tbi-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    background: rgba(245,166,35,0.1);
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,166,35,0.2);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .tbi-stat-val {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: #F5A623;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .tbi-stat-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }

  .fin-checks {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .fin-checks li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .afm-info-box {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  }

  .afm-info-box strong {
    display: block;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .afm-info-box ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .subsidies-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: #F5A623;
    color: #1A1A1A;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: background 0.15s, transform 0.15s;
  }

  .subsidies-cta:hover {
    background: #d4891a;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .subsidies-note {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
    margin-top: 0.6rem;
  }

  .subsidies-check-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }

  .subsidies-check-btn:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    color: white;
  }
</style>
